<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Folks this is a very high level item.  You have to win the lotto after beating the red dragon in a group or multi-groups most likely.  Do not try to save up for this.  I only know of one that was traded and this was the trade.  The person gave up the red dragon bp and efreeti boots for FULL myth armor set, 7 k pp, sword of skyfire, yak, and dwb's.  Enough said.  You may not think this is a good deal but for him it was as he got better stats and can get geb's again very soon.  The sword is one of the better ones on the game and the myth armor gave him better stats and we are talking about the full set of myth.  Sure one may not get as many gasps but looks do not make u great, stats do.  But no u will never see this item for sale.  It took alot of thought for this one to get traded.</font></td></tr></table>
